00:10:10,920 --> 00:10:13,832
Ti si Bejkerov?

3
00:10:22,560 --> 00:10:25,916
Reci Bejkeru da sam mu vec rekao
sve sto znam.

4
00:10:26,040 --> 00:10:30,591
Reci mu da zelim da zivim u miru.
Nema svrhe da me muci.

5
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:32,950
Ne znam nista o tom zlatu.

6
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:35,719
Sad je zlato nestalo.
Da je slusao,

7
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:38,479
izbegli bi ovaj sastanak.

8
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:42,593
Bio sam na vojnom sudu.
Nije bilo svedoka.

9
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:44,676
Nisu mogli da otkriju nista vise.

10
00:10:44,800 --> 00:10:47,712
Ne mogu da kazem Bejkeru sta 
se desilo sa novcem.

11
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:49,751
Vrati se i reci mu to.

12
00:10:50,880 --> 00:10:53,599
Prica se da si imao posetioca.

13
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:57,349
I Bejker zna to.

14
00:10:58,080 --> 00:11:00,992
Zove se Dzekson.

15
00:11:03,560 --> 00:11:05,152
Pa?

16
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:08,156
Dzekson je bio ovde.

17
00:11:08,760 --> 00:11:12,230
Ili Bejker gresi.

18
00:11:18,640 --> 00:11:20,551
Ne gresi.

19
00:11:20,680 --> 00:11:25,196
Mozda bi Bejker voleo da zna sta
ti i Dzekson imate da kazete

20
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:28,915
o kutiji sa parama.

21
00:11:31,520 --> 00:11:34,751
To nije ono za sta sam placen.

22
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:42,594
Samo me zanima pod kojim se imenom
Dzekson krije sada.

23
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:47,590
Zasto mislis da se Dzekson 
predstavlja sa laznim imenom?

24
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:49,790
Vec bih ga nasao do sada.

25
00:11:49,920 --> 00:11:53,754
Kad nekog pocnem da trazim,
onda ga i nadjem.

26
00:11:53,880 --> 00:11:56,235
Zato me placaju.

27
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:03,359
Ah... Zasto te Bejker placa?

28
00:12:05,520 --> 00:12:07,556
Je li to tvoja porodica?

29
00:12:15,800 --> 00:12:17,995
Da.

30
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:21,470
Fina porodica.

31
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:26,397
Koliko te placa da me ubijes?

32
00:12:28,640 --> 00:12:32,792
$500 - da dodjem do imena.

33
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:39,908
Ime!

34
00:12:48,680 --> 00:12:50,511
Karson.

35
00:12:50,640 --> 00:12:51,993
Bil Karson.

36
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:55,195
Tako se sad predstavlja.

37
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:27,070
Sav nas novac. 1000.

38
00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:33,275
1000 dolara?

39
00:13:34,680 --> 00:13:38,195
Nesto u zlatu. Pristojna suma.

40
00:13:41,520 --> 00:13:45,832
Kad sam placen,
uvek zavrsim posao.

41
00:14:55,120 --> 00:14:57,759
Ti si!

42
00:14:57,880 --> 00:14:59,950
Neka informacija?

43
00:15:00,880 --> 00:15:02,836
i previse.

44
00:15:02,960 --> 00:15:06,509
Rekao je dovoljno onog sto te
interesuje.

45
00:15:06,640 --> 00:15:09,313
I jos rec dve koje interesuju 
mene.

46
00:15:10,280 --> 00:15:11,633
Kao na preimer?

47
00:15:11,760 --> 00:15:16,276
Ime pod kojim se Dzekson krije
je Bil Karson.

48
00:15:16,640 --> 00:15:17,755
Ah.

49
00:15:18,480 --> 00:15:20,436
To je tvoj deo.

50
00:15:20,560 --> 00:15:24,314
Nastavi da pricas.

51
00:15:24,480 --> 00:15:28,439
Takodje je pomenuo nesto o
izvesnoj kutiji sa novcem,

52
00:15:28,560 --> 00:15:30,949
koja je izgleda nestala.

53
00:15:31,080 --> 00:15:32,798
To je moj deo.

54
00:15:32,920 --> 00:15:34,672
Jos nesto?

55
00:15:34,800 --> 00:15:38,076
Nije ti dosta, a?

56
00:15:38,200 --> 00:15:42,113
Pa, nemoj da brines.
Nikad vise nece nista reci.

57
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:44,196
O, da. Odlicno.

58
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:51,393
Evo... izvoli.
To je za tebe. Uradio si mi dobar posao.

59
00:15:51,560 --> 00:15:54,028
Vredi $500.

60
00:15:54,160 --> 00:15:59,188
Da. Umalo da zaboravim.

61
00:15:59,320 --> 00:16:01,231
Dao mi je 1000.

62
00:16:01,360 --> 00:16:04,591
Mislim da je hteo da te ja ubijem.

63
00:16:09,480 --> 00:16:12,950
Ali znas, steta je, kad sam placen

64
00:16:13,080 --> 00:16:15,196
uvek zavrsim posao.

65
00:16:15,320 --> 00:16:17,470
To znas.

66
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:19,238
Ne!

67
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:05,078
Ne. Ne pistolj, amigo.

68
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:08,556
Nece ti pomoci.
Trojica nas je.

69
00:17:22,800 --> 00:17:29,114
Hej, amigo, znas da imas lice dovoljno
lepo da vredi $2,000?

70
00:17:31,640 --> 00:17:33,358
Da,

71
00:17:33,480 --> 00:17:37,678
ali vi ne izgledate  kao oni koji
ce ga imati.

72
00:17:44,680 --> 00:17:46,955
Nekoliko koraka nazad.

73
00:18:38,520 --> 00:18:40,397
Hvala.

74
00:18:48,560 --> 00:18:50,630
Koliko sada vredis?

75
00:18:50,760 --> 00:18:52,830
Koliko?

76
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:55,595
$2,000!

77
00:18:57,200 --> 00:19:00,192
Tacno, $2,000.

78
00:19:00,320 --> 00:19:02,515
Da. $2,000!

79
00:19:08,400 --> 00:19:11,676
Hijo de puta que tu pario.
Platices!

80
00:19:11,800 --> 00:19:14,234
Dabog da zavrsis na groblju,

81
00:19:14,920 --> 00:19:17,753
sa kolerom, besnilom i kugom!

82
00:19:17,880 --> 00:19:19,279
Oslobodi me.

83
00:19:19,400 --> 00:19:22,358
Oslobodi me, ti prljavo kopile!
Pusi me!

84
00:19:22,480 --> 00:19:26,155
Dabog da ti majka zavrsi
u jeftinom kupleraju!

85
00:19:26,440 --> 00:19:28,317
Pusti me!

86
00:19:28,440 --> 00:19:32,433
Jos uvek mozes da se spasis.
Pusti me i oprosticu ti.

87
00:19:32,560 --> 00:19:34,676
Pusti me!

88
00:19:34,800 --> 00:19:39,828
Lose mi je.
Sva krv mi je u mozgu.

89
00:19:39,960 --> 00:19:44,192
Zedan sam, Bel. Vode... Vode...

90
00:19:50,320 --> 00:19:51,833
Zmijo!

91
00:19:52,200 --> 00:19:54,760
Kuckin sine! Pusti me!

92
00:19:55,000 --> 00:19:58,709
Hrabar si pored vezanog coveka!
Vracaj se!

93
00:19:58,840 --> 00:20:01,274
Vracaj se i bori se!

94
00:20:01,400 --> 00:20:03,038
Kopile!

95
00:20:04,560 --> 00:20:08,235
Ko je to, dovraga?
Jedno djubre udje, drugo izadje.

96
00:20:08,360 --> 00:20:13,150
- Prekini!
- Ja sam casni farmer. Nevin sam.

97
00:20:14,840 --> 00:20:17,400
Znaci ti si posteni farmer?

98
00:20:17,520 --> 00:20:19,829
Jel prepoznajes ovog?

99
00:20:19,960 --> 00:20:22,269
Aha. To si ti.

100
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:26,234
Ja? Ko to kaze? Ne znas ni da citas.

101
00:20:26,360 --> 00:20:31,275
Urolaj ga. Dacu ti dobru ideju
gde da ga turis!

102
00:20:31,400 --> 00:20:35,234
Do vraga svi serifi i zamenici
i ko vam dade znacku.

103
00:20:35,360 --> 00:20:39,319
Hej, pogledajte ...
Daje mu prljav novac.

104
00:20:39,440 --> 00:20:43,353
Judas! Ti si me prodao.
Ali neces uzivati u tom novcu.

105
00:20:43,480 --> 00:20:47,359
Ako ima pravde na svetu,
taj novac ce kod grobara.

106
00:20:47,480 --> 00:20:49,072
Znas ko si ti?

107
00:20:49,200 --> 00:20:51,270
Hoces da znas ciji si ti sin?

108
00:20:51,400 --> 00:20:55,188
Ne znas. Ja znam. Svi znaju.
Ti si sin hiljadu oceva.

109
00:20:55,320 --> 00:20:57,356
I svi su prokletnici kao ti.

110
00:20:57,480 --> 00:20:59,789
A tvoja majka, ona je...

111
00:20:59,920 --> 00:21:02,195
Kopile!

112
00:21:02,320 --> 00:21:05,153
Tvojoj majci... Bolje da ne 
pricam o njoj!

113
00:21:05,280 --> 00:21:06,998
Ja nikad nisam povredio nikoga!

114
00:21:07,200 --> 00:21:13,070
Trazen u 14 drzava,
osudjeni je kriv

115
00:21:13,200 --> 00:21:19,548
za ubistvo, oruzanu pljacku gradjana,
drzavnih banaka, i posta,

116
00:21:19,680 --> 00:21:23,798
pljacku crkvenih objekata, 

117
00:21:23,920 --> 00:21:28,471
krivokletstvo, dvozenstvo,
napustanje zene i dece,

118
00:21:28,600 --> 00:21:30,955
podsticanje prostitucije, otmicu,

119
00:21:31,080 --> 00:21:34,993
iznudu, kupovinu kradene robe,
prodaju kradene robe,

120
00:21:35,120 --> 00:21:37,190
sirenje laznog novca

121
00:21:37,320 --> 00:21:39,675
i suprotno zakonu,

122
00:21:39,800 --> 00:21:42,917
optuzeni je kriv za koriscenje
oznacenih karata...

123
00:21:45,200 --> 00:21:50,433
Za navedeno osudjujemo optuzenog,

124
00:21:50,560 --> 00:21:55,350
Tuka Benedikta Pacifija
Huan-Maria Ramireza,

125
00:21:55,480 --> 00:21:57,391
Poznatog kao "Pacov".

126
00:22:00,000 --> 00:22:03,356
na smrt vesanjem.
Neka se Bog smiluje njegovoj dusi.

127
00:22:03,480 --> 00:22:05,277
Nastavi!

128
00:22:29,760 --> 00:22:32,957
5 za tebe.

129
00:22:33,360 --> 00:22:36,477
1, 2, 3, 4,... 5 za mene.

130
00:22:37,760 --> 00:22:41,833
5 za tebe... i 5 za mene.

131
00:22:41,960 --> 00:22:45,191
Znas koliko sada vredis?

132
00:22:45,320 --> 00:22:48,437
- Ne. Koliko?
- $3,000.

133
00:22:50,440 --> 00:22:54,353
Ima dve vrste ljudi na svetu,
moj prijatelju,

134
00:22:54,480 --> 00:22:58,837
oni sa uzetom oko vrata i oni
koji dele zaradu.

135
00:22:59,520 --> 00:23:04,116
Vrat oko kojeg je uze je moj.
Ja podnosim rizik.

136
00:23:04,240 --> 00:23:07,391
Sledeci put hocu vise od pola.

137
00:23:07,520 --> 00:23:12,230
Mozda ti rizikujes, prijatelju,
ali ja sam taj koji deli.

138
00:23:13,240 --> 00:23:18,268
Da smanjimo moj procenat... Cigaru?

139
00:23:20,640 --> 00:23:22,835
Mozda cu onda losije da nisanim.

140
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:27,988
Mm... Ali ako promasis,
promasi dobro.

141
00:23:28,120 --> 00:23:32,079
Ko god me promasi i ostavi me 
da zivim,

142
00:23:32,200 --> 00:23:35,237
on ne zna nista o Tuku.

143
00:23:36,400 --> 00:23:37,628
Nista!

144
00:23:41,760 --> 00:23:43,876
Trazen u 15 drzava,

145
00:23:44,000 --> 00:23:50,155
vec osudjen, Tuko
Benedikto Pacifiko Juan-Maria Ramirez,

146
00:23:50,320 --> 00:23:54,677
je kriv za sledece zlocine:

147
00:23:54,800 --> 00:23:58,588
Ubistvo, nasrtaj, silovanje
device bele rase,

148
00:23:58,720 --> 00:24:02,030
silovanje maloletnice crne rase,

149
00:24:03,960 --> 00:24:07,839
- prevrtanje voza...
- Hej, Lepooki!

150
00:24:12,160 --> 00:24:14,196
Sta si otkrio, Kratki?

151
00:24:14,320 --> 00:24:16,151
Lici na knjigu!

152
00:24:16,320 --> 00:24:22,759
Jedinica koja je pratila novac je upala
u Jenki zasedu i samo su trojica spasena.

153
00:24:22,880 --> 00:24:25,075
Stivens, Bejker, and Dzekson.

154
00:24:25,200 --> 00:24:28,158
Ono sto nije spaseno je novac.

155
00:24:28,280 --> 00:24:32,319
Vojska organizuje saslusanje,
i Dzekson je oslobodjen.

156
00:24:32,440 --> 00:24:34,476
Onda nestaje i postaje Bil Karson.

157
00:24:34,600 --> 00:24:38,388
- Znam njegovo ime.
- Ali neznas koga trazis. Ja znam.

158
00:24:38,520 --> 00:24:41,876
A kad bude pronadjen,
ne bih bio u njegovoj kozi.

159
00:24:43,960 --> 00:24:45,837
Gde je Karson?

160
00:24:45,960 --> 00:24:49,430
Sve sto znam, Karson je ponovo u vojsci.
Jadnicak je izgubio oko.

161
00:24:49,560 --> 00:24:53,269
Zivi sa devojkom koja se zove Maria.
Ona je nova, mlada kurva.

162
00:24:53,400 --> 00:24:56,437
- Gde je ona?
- Kako se ono zvase grad?

163
00:24:56,560 --> 00:24:58,232
Negde prilicno blizu.

164
00:25:00,560 --> 00:25:01,913
Santa Ana.

165
00:25:04,240 --> 00:25:07,869
Adios, polovino.

166
00:25:11,200 --> 00:25:13,350
Hej, Luk, spusti mi jedan viski!

167
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:27,350
Drago mi je sto su ga uhvatili.
Covek koji je sve ono uradio.

168
00:25:27,480 --> 00:25:32,235
- Osudjene ljude ne obese uvek.
- Kako to mislite?

169
00:25:32,360 --> 00:25:36,478
Cak i prljavi prosjak kao on ima
svog andjela cuvara.

170
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:45,470
Zlatnokosi andjeo pazi na njega.

171
00:25:45,600 --> 00:25:49,354
Za ove zlocine,
optuzeni je dao priznanje.

172
00:25:50,160 --> 00:25:54,517
Zato ga osudjujemo na smrt vesanjem.

173
00:25:54,640 --> 00:25:56,949
Neka mu se bog smiluje.
Nastavite.

174
00:26:11,240 --> 00:26:13,913
Brisimo odavde!

175
00:26:44,200 --> 00:26:46,270
Svako moze da promasi?!

176
00:26:46,400 --> 00:26:49,358
Niko ne moze dok sam ja sa omcom.

177
00:26:49,480 --> 00:26:51,948
Nikad je nisi imao oko vrata.

178
00:26:52,080 --> 00:26:57,234
Kad uze pocne da se zateze,
osetis kako te je djavo ujeo za dupe.

179
00:26:58,280 --> 00:27:00,669
Da. U pravu si.

180
00:27:00,800 --> 00:27:03,792
Postaje zajebano.

181
00:27:03,920 --> 00:27:09,597
Kako ja shvatam, nema buducnosti
sa propalicom kao ti.

182
00:27:09,720 --> 00:27:11,551
Kako to mislis?

183
00:27:11,680 --> 00:27:15,355
Mislim da nikad neces vredeti vise
od $3,000.

184
00:27:15,480 --> 00:27:17,630
Sta to znaci?

185
00:27:17,760 --> 00:27:21,070
Znaci da je nase partnerstvo gotovo.

186
00:27:22,520 --> 00:27:24,750
Oh, ne, ne ti. Ti ostajes vezan.

187
00:27:24,880 --> 00:27:28,111
Ja cu zadrzati pare.
Ti zadrzi konopac.

188
00:27:28,240 --> 00:27:30,959
Prljavo, prevaranstko kopile!

189
00:27:31,080 --> 00:27:35,790
- Smrdljivi...
- Do sledeceg grada je samo 70 milja.

190
00:27:35,920 --> 00:27:39,913
Ako stedis dah, osecam da mozes uspeti.

191
00:27:40,040 --> 00:27:42,713
Adios.

192
00:27:42,840 --> 00:27:44,876
Prljavo kopile! Vracaj se!

193
00:27:45,840 --> 00:27:50,152
Oslobodi me!
Silazi sa konja, bedna kukavice!

194
00:27:50,280 --> 00:27:53,352
Ako te ikad uhvatim, izcupacu ti srce i
pojesti ga zivog!

195
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:57,959
Odracu te zivog. Obesicu te za muda!
Lesinaru!

196
00:27:58,320 --> 00:28:00,709
Ubicu te... Ubicu te!

197
00:28:01,840 --> 00:28:06,994
Takva nezahvalnost!
Toliko puta sam ti spasao zivot.

198
00:28:13,960 --> 00:28:18,158
Ovo je samo sala. Neces me ostaviti.
Vracaj se! Cekaj!

199
00:28:18,280 --> 00:28:20,714
Slusaj, Beli!

200
00:28:20,840 --> 00:28:26,153
Hijo de una gran puta!

201
00:28:44,800 --> 00:28:47,598
Verujem da je gospodja kod kuce.

202
00:28:47,720 --> 00:28:50,075
Laku noc!

203
00:28:58,360 --> 00:29:01,830
Prokleti pacovi!

204
00:29:17,200 --> 00:29:18,394
Marija!

205
00:29:24,880 --> 00:29:27,030
Jesi li ti, Bil?

206
00:29:28,000 --> 00:29:29,877
Bil!

207
00:29:37,600 --> 00:29:39,556
Ko si ti?

208
00:29:39,760 --> 00:29:41,751
Sta hoces samnom?

209
00:29:42,240 --> 00:29:45,198
Nastavi da pricas o Bilu Karsonu.

210
00:29:45,320 --> 00:29:47,231
Ne znam.

211
00:29:47,400 --> 00:29:51,109
Njega si zvala u mraku.

212
00:29:54,800 --> 00:29:56,711
Gde je?

213
00:29:56,840 --> 00:29:58,956
Sta ces uciniti samnom?

214
00:30:00,560 --> 00:30:02,391
Ja postavljam pitanja.

215
00:30:04,200 --> 00:30:06,111
Gde je?

216
00:30:13,160 --> 00:30:14,798
Gde je?

217
00:30:15,600 --> 00:30:18,558
Gde? Gde? Gde?

218
00:30:21,640 --> 00:30:23,392
Dosta!

219
00:30:24,080 --> 00:30:28,073
Ne znam gde je.
Spakovao je svoje stvari pre deset dana.

220
00:30:28,280 --> 00:30:31,272
Otisao je sa svojom jedinicom. Svi su otisli.

221
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:34,198
Kakva jedinica? Gde je otisao?

222
00:30:36,560 --> 00:30:38,039
Hm?

223
00:30:38,160 --> 00:30:42,790
Treca Konjicka.
General Sibli. Za Santa Fe.

224
00:30:42,920 --> 00:30:44,911
To je sve sto znam.

225
00:30:45,040 --> 00:30:47,952
Kunem se.

226
00:32:15,120 --> 00:32:18,476
Vrlo mi je zao, ali radnja se zatvara.

227
00:32:29,040 --> 00:32:30,189
Hej!

228
00:32:53,560 --> 00:32:56,279
- Revolveri!
- Da, revolvers.

229
00:33:00,840 --> 00:33:02,193
Revolveri!

230
00:33:02,320 --> 00:33:06,154
Evo, ovde drzim najbolje.

231
00:33:11,160 --> 00:33:13,754
Evo, Remington, Colt,

232
00:33:13,880 --> 00:33:17,111
Herut, Smit-Weson,

233
00:33:17,240 --> 00:33:21,313
Colt - mornaricki, Dzoslin,

234
00:33:21,440 --> 00:33:24,876
- jos jedan Remington, i ovaj...
- To je dosta.

235
00:34:06,000 --> 00:34:07,353
Municija.

236
00:34:16,840 --> 00:34:21,675
- Ako hocete da probate, izadjite napolje.
- Haj'mo.

237
00:34:25,240 --> 00:34:27,071
Mrdaj, mrdaj!

238
00:35:39,000 --> 00:35:40,877
Metak.

239
00:35:48,360 --> 00:35:50,999
- Koliko?
- $20.

240
00:35:53,720 --> 00:35:55,756
Ne!

241
00:35:57,280 --> 00:35:59,032
$50.

242
00:35:59,600 --> 00:36:04,310
- Koliko?
- $100.

243
00:36:06,840 --> 00:36:10,150
$200. To je sve sto imam.

244
00:36:10,280 --> 00:36:11,838
Evo.

245
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:32,558
Dodji ovamo.

246
00:36:39,440 --> 00:36:41,476
- Aaa!
- Aaa!

247
00:37:01,720 --> 00:37:04,632
Jutros sam cuo celu pricu.

248
00:37:04,760 --> 00:37:08,116
Pukovnik Kambei se priblizava
sa svojim severnjacima.

249
00:37:08,240 --> 00:37:11,437
Zato ovi juznjaci odlaze.

250
00:37:11,560 --> 00:37:14,836
Cim ove kukavice cuju za plave
bluze, pobegnu.

251
00:37:15,600 --> 00:37:18,831
- Ne zele da se bore.
- Jadnici.

252
00:37:18,960 --> 00:37:20,791
Uskoro su gotovi.

253
00:37:20,920 --> 00:37:23,514
Onda mozemo da zaradjujemo na 
onim Jenkijima.

254
00:37:23,640 --> 00:37:26,154
Oni imaju zlato, ne papirne dolare.

255
00:37:26,280 --> 00:37:28,999
I pobedice Jug.

256
00:37:29,120 --> 00:37:34,035
Vidite onog sa belom bradom,
General Sibli? Izgleda mrtav.

257
00:37:34,160 --> 00:37:36,594
Konacno nas ostavlja na miru.

258
00:37:36,720 --> 00:37:40,156
Ura za Diksija!
Ura, ura za Diksija!

259
00:37:43,720 --> 00:37:46,553
Gde je vlasnik onog konja?

260
00:37:46,680 --> 00:37:50,036
- Molim vas, gospodine... A lose srce...
- Gde je?

261
00:37:50,160 --> 00:37:55,359
- Rat me je vec prestavio.
- Hocu vlasnika onog konja.

262
00:37:55,480 --> 00:38:00,315
On je visok, plav, pusi cigare
i svinja je. Gde je sada?

263
00:38:00,440 --> 00:38:03,159
Ostavi ga, on ne zna bas svakoga
stranca.

264
00:38:03,280 --> 00:38:05,919
Ti cuti, matora kokosko.

265
00:38:06,040 --> 00:38:09,999
Gore. Gore u sobi 4, gospodine.

266
00:38:15,680 --> 00:38:17,477
Cujes to?

267
00:38:21,880 --> 00:38:26,112
- Kriminalci. Kako se usudjujete?!
- Ssh!

268
00:41:15,800 --> 00:41:17,756
Tvoje mamuze.

269
00:41:29,040 --> 00:41:33,431
Ima dve vrste mamuza.
One koje udju kroz vrata,

270
00:41:33,560 --> 00:41:36,313
i one koje udju kroz prozor.

271
00:41:36,440 --> 00:41:38,590
Skini taj opasac.

272
00:41:45,680 --> 00:41:47,716
Prazan je.

273
00:41:49,720 --> 00:41:51,472
Moj nije.

274
00:41:56,680 --> 00:42:01,800
Cak i kad se Juda obesio,
bila je oluja.

275
00:42:05,000 --> 00:42:07,275
Mozda je topovska paljba.

276
00:42:07,400 --> 00:42:10,198
Sta god, tebi je isto.

277
00:42:12,200 --> 00:42:15,431
Jesi li video nekad ovo, prijatelju?

278
00:42:23,720 --> 00:42:27,759
Baci ovo preko krovne grede.

279
00:42:28,760 --> 00:42:30,113
Tako.

280
00:42:41,400 --> 00:42:43,197
Penji se.

281
00:42:51,960 --> 00:42:53,916
Odlicno!

282
00:42:54,040 --> 00:42:56,076
Proveri da li je konopac zategnut.

283
00:42:56,440 --> 00:42:59,750
Mora da izdrzi tezinu svinje.

284
00:43:05,320 --> 00:43:07,914
Sad stavi omcu oko vrata.

285
00:43:14,280 --> 00:43:16,510
Odlicno.

286
00:43:16,720 --> 00:43:19,234
Prevelika za tvoj vrat, a?

287
00:43:19,360 --> 00:43:22,796
Sad cemo to da sredimo.
Imam drugi sistem.

288
00:43:22,920 --> 00:43:25,718
Malo drugaciji od tvog.

289
00:43:26,480 --> 00:43:30,632
Necu pucati u konopac,
nego u noge od stolice.

290
00:43:34,360 --> 00:43:36,032
Adios!

291
00:46:27,280 --> 00:46:30,955
Nasli smo da je optuzeni,
Tomas Larson, alias Sorti Larson,

292
00:46:31,200 --> 00:46:34,431
kriv za sledece zlocine:

293
00:46:34,560 --> 00:46:38,189
kardja konja, kradja vojnih 
rezervi Juznjacke armije,...

294
00:46:45,480 --> 00:46:48,392
..krivokletstvo, ucena, pljacka...

295
00:46:51,280 --> 00:46:53,111
A Sorti?

296
00:46:57,840 --> 00:46:59,671
Ne.

297
00:46:59,800 --> 00:47:01,313
Ne?

298
00:47:06,240 --> 00:47:10,313
Neka se Bog smiluje njegovoj dusi.
Nastavite.

299
00:47:16,040 --> 00:47:18,031
Zao mi je, Sorti.

300
00:47:19,040 --> 00:47:20,996
Mrdaj. Idemo.

301
00:47:44,920 --> 00:47:48,879
Ne znam...
Cim se nadjem u pustinji,ozednim.

302
00:47:49,000 --> 00:47:53,710
Kazu da ljudi sa svetlim tenom ne
mogu da je podnesu.

303
00:48:17,040 --> 00:48:19,793
Bolje, neces morati da nosis
nista tesko!

304
00:48:20,760 --> 00:48:22,796
Gde cemo?

305
00:48:22,920 --> 00:48:24,239
Gde?

306
00:48:24,720 --> 00:48:26,676
Gde ja idem, amigo.

307
00:48:26,800 --> 00:48:28,995
Onuda.

308
00:48:29,120 --> 00:48:32,157
Jos 100 milja lepe suncane
pustinje.

309
00:48:32,280 --> 00:48:36,034
Cak se i armija plasi da prodje
ovuda.

310
00:48:36,160 --> 00:48:38,469
Siblijevi ljudi se povlace gore.

311
00:48:38,600 --> 00:48:40,636
Kambijevi dolaze odande.

312
00:48:40,760 --> 00:48:44,719
Ali niko ne ide ovim paklom.

313
00:48:44,840 --> 00:48:47,673
Osim tebe... i mene.

314
00:48:48,040 --> 00:48:51,430
100 milja - to je lepa setnja.

315
00:48:53,440 --> 00:48:57,353
Sta si mi ono rekao prosli put?

316
00:48:58,720 --> 00:49:00,836
Ako stedis dah,

317
00:49:00,960 --> 00:49:04,714
osecam da ces uspeti!

318
00:49:05,440 --> 00:49:09,638
A ako ne uspes,umreces... sporo.

319
00:49:09,760 --> 00:49:13,355
Vrlo sporo, prijatelju.

320
00:49:18,080 --> 00:49:20,674
Posle tebe, molim. Kreni.

321
00:51:11,280 --> 00:51:13,874
Odmaras?

322
00:51:15,000 --> 00:51:19,516
Ajde, Beli.
Ne idemo daleko. Samo 70 milja.

323
00:51:19,680 --> 00:51:23,992
Samo 8,5 sati do sumraka.

324
00:51:24,120 --> 00:51:26,873
Nije lose.

325
00:51:27,560 --> 00:51:29,118
Hajde.

326
00:52:11,360 --> 00:52:12,679
Oh!

327
00:53:26,680 --> 00:53:28,716
I tako, Beli,

328
00:53:31,680 --> 00:53:33,636
to je zbogom!

329
00:54:27,080 --> 00:54:29,275
Hoa, hoa!

330
00:54:34,200 --> 00:54:35,952
Polako, polako.

331
00:54:36,080 --> 00:54:37,911
Polako.

332
00:56:59,280 --> 00:57:02,272
Vode...

333
00:57:10,360 --> 00:57:15,878
200,000 u zlatu - tvoje je.
Samo mi daj vode.

334
00:57:19,160 --> 00:57:21,116
O cemu pricas?

335
00:57:21,240 --> 00:57:24,789
- Ko si ti, dovraga?
- Karson.

336
00:57:24,920 --> 00:57:27,639
Moje ime je Bil Karson sada.

337
00:57:27,760 --> 00:57:29,796
Zaseda.

338
00:57:30,320 --> 00:57:32,914
Svi mrtvi.

339
00:57:33,040 --> 00:57:35,349
Zovem se Dzekson, ne, Karson...

340
00:57:35,480 --> 00:57:39,109
Karson. Da. Drago mi je,
ja sam Linkolnov deda.

341
00:57:39,240 --> 00:57:44,234
- Sta si rekao za dolare?
- 200,000 sve moje.

342
00:57:44,360 --> 00:57:45,918
Bilo je od Trece Konjicke.

343
00:57:46,240 --> 00:57:48,629
Bejker nema nista.

344
00:57:48,760 --> 00:57:53,754
Zlato... Sakrio sam zlato.
Zlato je na sigurnom.

345
00:57:53,880 --> 00:57:56,758
Gde? Gde? Ovde?

346
00:57:57,520 --> 00:58:00,876
- Pricaj!
- Groblje...

347
00:58:01,640 --> 00:58:04,029
Koje groblje?

348
00:58:04,200 --> 00:58:09,228
Ono ... na... Sed Hilu.
Tamo... u grobu...

349
00:58:09,360 --> 00:58:12,272
Kom grobu? Neko ime?

350
00:58:12,400 --> 00:58:14,550
Neki broj? Ajde!

351
00:58:14,720 --> 00:58:21,114
- Pricaj!
- Nema broj. Samo ... ime.

352
00:58:21,240 --> 00:58:23,515
- Ha?
- Pise...

353
00:58:30,520 --> 00:58:32,158
V... vode...

354
00:58:33,080 --> 00:58:37,119
Prvo pricaj. Dacu ti vode posle.

355
00:58:37,240 --> 00:58:39,356
Sed Hil groblje. OK.

356
00:58:39,480 --> 00:58:41,118
U grobu. OK.

357
00:58:41,240 --> 00:58:45,995
Mora imati broj ili ime.
Mora da ima 1,000... 5,000...

358
00:58:46,200 --> 00:58:48,509
Vode...

359
00:58:49,040 --> 00:58:53,431
Nemoj umreti. Nemoj. Donecu ti vode.

360
00:58:53,840 --> 00:58:57,515
Stani tu. Ne mrdaj. Donecu ti vode.

361
00:58:57,640 --> 00:58:59,676
Umri kasnije!

362
00:59:23,560 --> 00:59:25,437
Odlazi odavde!

363
00:59:31,320 --> 00:59:32,958
Mrtav je!

364
00:59:36,280 --> 00:59:38,271
Ubicu te.

365
00:59:39,520 --> 00:59:43,752
Ako to uradis, uvek biti bedan

366
00:59:43,880 --> 00:59:47,634
kao pacov, sto i jesi.

367
00:59:48,240 --> 00:59:52,233
Na tvom mestu, drzao bi me u zivotu.

368
00:59:52,360 --> 00:59:54,510
Sta ti je, dovraga, rekao?

369
00:59:54,640 --> 00:59:58,155
- Ime.
- ?!?

370
00:59:58,280 --> 01:00:01,511
- Ime sa groba.
- Koje ime?

371
01:00:15,000 --> 01:00:17,150
Beli, nemoj umreti.

372
01:00:17,360 --> 01:00:19,510
Beli, nemoj umreti.

373
01:00:19,640 --> 01:00:21,710
Ja sam tvoj prijatelj. Molim te,
nemoj da umres.

374
01:00:21,840 --> 01:00:23,910
Ja sam ti prijatelj. Hajde!

375
01:00:24,920 --> 01:00:29,596
Beli, pomoci cu ti. Pomoci cu ti!

376
01:00:29,720 --> 01:00:32,359
Ne mrdaj! Vracam se odmah.

377
01:00:32,480 --> 01:00:34,311
Nemoj da umres kao svinja.

378
01:00:34,440 --> 01:00:38,149
Beli, voda. Voda, Beli.

379
01:00:38,280 --> 01:00:40,316
Nemoj da pijes, nije dobro za tebe.

380
01:00:40,440 --> 01:00:45,230
Beli, sta ti je?
Nemoj umreti.

381
01:01:08,360 --> 01:01:09,679
Hoa!

382
01:01:12,360 --> 01:01:14,271
Imam vrlo bolesnog coveka.

383
01:01:14,400 --> 01:01:17,597
- Ali vise nemamo kreveta.
- Daj mu svoj.

384
01:01:22,680 --> 01:01:27,310
- Gde je Otac Ramirez?
- Trenutno je na putu.

385
01:01:27,440 --> 01:01:29,431
Ocekujemo ga svaki dan.

386
01:01:29,560 --> 01:01:33,075
Nema veze.
Dobro cemo paziti mog prijatelja.

387
01:01:33,200 --> 01:01:35,350
I neka je slavljen bog.

388
01:01:35,480 --> 01:01:41,112
Bof je na nasoj strani, zato
mrzi Jenkije. Jel' tako, Beli?

389
01:01:41,240 --> 01:01:45,074
- Oce, dise li?
- Da, naravno.

390
01:01:57,560 --> 01:01:58,959
Ovamo.

391
01:02:28,200 --> 01:02:30,430
Stavite mu novu presvlaku.

392
01:02:31,280 --> 01:02:33,840
Daj gu u moju odaju.

393
01:02:39,080 --> 01:02:41,514
Napolje, vojnice. Izadji. Hajde.

394
01:02:41,640 --> 01:02:44,677
Pazite ga, molim vas.
On mi je kao brat.

395
01:02:49,520 --> 01:02:51,158
Hej, Oce, ja...

396
01:03:03,080 --> 01:03:05,469
Oce, da li govori?
Je li rekao nesto?

397
01:03:34,480 --> 01:03:38,359
Oce, da li trazi za mene?
Je li rekao nesto?

398
01:03:38,480 --> 01:03:40,357
Oh, ne. Jos nista.

399
01:03:40,480 --> 01:03:44,473
Ali, mlad je i jak -
to ce ga spasiti.

400
01:03:44,600 --> 01:03:47,512
Povratice snagu ubrzo.

401
01:03:47,640 --> 01:03:50,791
Hvala. Ne znate sta mi on znaci!

402
01:03:50,920 --> 01:03:52,194
Hvala Isusu!

403
01:04:38,840 --> 01:04:40,114
Beli?

404
01:04:45,400 --> 01:04:46,549
Hej, Beli...

405
01:04:46,680 --> 01:04:48,113
Beli.

406
01:05:05,840 --> 01:05:10,516
Otac mi kaze da ces za nekoliko
dana biti na nogama.

407
01:05:10,640 --> 01:05:14,428
Imao si srece sto si imao mene
tako blizu... kad se to desilo.

408
01:05:14,560 --> 01:05:16,710
Zamisli da si bio sam.

409
01:05:18,200 --> 01:05:22,796
Vidis, kad je neko... bolestan,

410
01:05:22,920 --> 01:05:26,993
dobro je da ima nekog,
prijatelje ili rodbinu.

411
01:05:27,120 --> 01:05:31,875
Imas li roditelje, Beli?

412
01:05:32,000 --> 01:05:33,399
Majku?

413
01:05:33,680 --> 01:05:36,194
Cak ni majku.

414
01:05:36,600 --> 01:05:38,079
Nikog?

415
01:05:38,200 --> 01:05:42,159
Bio si sam, jel'? Kao ja.

416
01:05:42,280 --> 01:05:44,635
Bili smo sami na svetu.

417
01:05:44,760 --> 01:05:47,752
Ja imam tebe. Ti imas mene.

418
01:05:47,880 --> 01:05:51,509
Samo za kratko, mislim.

419
01:05:51,800 --> 01:05:53,916
Tako mora biti.

420
01:05:54,160 --> 01:05:57,550
Kakav prljav, pokvaren trik sudbine.

421
01:05:57,680 --> 01:06:00,831
Mogli smo imati sav novac u 
svojim rukama.

422
01:06:03,560 --> 01:06:08,839
Ja... moram ti reci istinu, Beli.

423
01:06:08,960 --> 01:06:12,077
Na mom mestu, ti bi uradio istu stvar.

424
01:06:12,200 --> 01:06:15,670
Sve... sve je gotovo za tebe.

425
01:06:15,800 --> 01:06:19,429
Niko vise nista ne moze da ucini.

426
01:06:23,480 --> 01:06:27,314
To je moja greska... moja... moja... moja... moja.

427
01:06:35,960 --> 01:06:38,713
Reci cu ti nesto, Beli...

428
01:06:38,840 --> 01:06:42,276
Da ja znam da mi je kraj,

429
01:06:42,400 --> 01:06:46,279
kunem se, na mom mestu...
na tvom mestu, uradio bih istu stvar.

430
01:06:46,400 --> 01:06:50,075
Rekao bih za zlato.
Da, da, rekao bih.

431
01:06:50,200 --> 01:06:52,270
Rekao bih ime groba.

432
01:06:52,440 --> 01:06:54,635
Sta ce ti novac kad si mrtav?

433
01:06:54,760 --> 01:06:56,716
Znam koje je groblje.

434
01:06:56,840 --> 01:07:00,958
Ali, znas koliko grobova ima tamo?

435
01:07:01,080 --> 01:07:05,073
Beli, molim te. Uzmi malo...

436
01:07:08,840 --> 01:07:11,673
Molim te, reci mi ime.

437
01:07:11,800 --> 01:07:15,156
Sa... sa groba.

438
01:07:15,280 --> 01:07:19,512
Ako nadjem 200,000 dolara,

439
01:07:19,640 --> 01:07:22,473
uvek cu te se secati.

440
01:07:22,600 --> 01:07:26,673
Kunem se, uvek cu te se secati.

441
01:07:28,600 --> 01:07:30,750
Pridji... blize.

442
01:07:35,840 --> 01:07:37,114
Reci!

443
01:07:39,400 --> 01:07:40,355
Ti prljavi...

444
01:07:42,840 --> 01:07:44,910
Spavacu bolje,

445
01:07:45,040 --> 01:07:49,636
ako znam da mi je prijatelj
blizu...

446
01:07:49,760 --> 01:07:51,955
da me zastiti.

447
01:08:02,120 --> 01:08:03,758
"Tuko, vode!"

448
01:08:03,920 --> 01:08:07,196
ali ako dobijem to ime od tebe,
dacu ti vodu!

449
01:08:14,280 --> 01:08:17,989
U redu, prljavi tvore,
dizi dupe s kreveta. 'Ajde.

450
01:08:18,120 --> 01:08:21,635
Zabava je gotova.
Kola su spremna da krenu.

451
01:08:21,760 --> 01:08:25,912
Bolje da nestanemo,
pre nego sto nas uhvati rat.

452
01:08:26,040 --> 01:08:28,235
Tuco, Otac Ramirez se vratio.

453
01:08:29,280 --> 01:08:33,717
Nesto moram da vidim.
Bice kratko. Spremaj se.

454
01:08:33,840 --> 01:08:36,229
- Kuda? Ovuda?
- Da.

455
01:08:51,520 --> 01:08:53,078
Hej, Pablo?

456
01:09:00,800 --> 01:09:03,439
Zar me ne prepoznajes?

457
01:09:03,560 --> 01:09:06,996
To sam ja. Tuko!

458
01:09:07,520 --> 01:09:11,354
Da te zagrlim... ooh!

459
01:09:12,640 --> 01:09:15,234
Ne znam kako!

460
01:09:19,280 --> 01:09:23,717
Bio sam usput. Reko', "Pitam se
da li me se moj brat seca?"

461
01:09:26,680 --> 01:09:28,750
Jesam li pogresio?

462
01:09:30,200 --> 01:09:32,998
Nema veze. Vrlo sam srecan!

463
01:09:33,120 --> 01:09:35,236
Video si me, Tuko.

464
01:09:36,160 --> 01:09:39,914
Da, pa, vrlo mi je drago sto sam
tu.

465
01:09:43,880 --> 01:09:46,997
Ah, moja uniforma!

466
01:09:47,120 --> 01:09:50,192
Duga prica! Ali pricaj mi o tebi.

467
01:09:50,320 --> 01:09:54,233
To je vaznije. Izgledas vrlo dobro.

468
01:09:54,360 --> 01:09:57,079
Malo mrsav, mozda, ali...

469
01:09:58,240 --> 01:10:02,153
uvek si bio mrsav, jel, Pablito?

470
01:10:03,400 --> 01:10:06,198
Pa, kako su nam roditelji?

471
01:10:07,280 --> 01:10:12,115
Tek sada mislis na njih.
Posle devet godina.

472
01:10:15,040 --> 01:10:17,235
Mm. Devet godina?

473
01:10:17,360 --> 01:10:20,432
Pa dobro, devet godina!

474
01:10:20,560 --> 01:10:22,118
Devet godina!

475
01:10:22,320 --> 01:10:25,471
Nasa majka je mrtva vec dugo.

476
01:10:26,800 --> 01:10:32,193
Nas otac je umro pre nekoliko dana.
Zato sam bio odsutan.

477
01:10:33,160 --> 01:10:35,116
Trazio je da ti budes tamo.

478
01:10:35,280 --> 01:10:38,113
Ali bio sam samo ja.

479
01:10:44,120 --> 01:10:46,509
A ti?

480
01:10:47,120 --> 01:10:50,430
Pored zla, sta si jos postigao?

481
01:10:50,560 --> 01:10:54,314
Cini mi se da si nekada imao zenu.

482
01:10:57,000 --> 01:10:59,195
Ne jednu. Mnogo njih.

483
01:10:59,320 --> 01:11:02,198
Jednu ovde, jednu tamo,
gde god hocu.

484
01:11:03,080 --> 01:11:05,719
'Ajde, popuj mi, Pablo.

485
01:11:05,840 --> 01:11:08,832
Cemu?

486
01:11:08,960 --> 01:11:12,430
Samo nastavi tako.

487
01:11:12,560 --> 01:11:14,471
Idi.

488
01:11:14,600 --> 01:11:16,795
Neka ti se bog smiluje.

489
01:11:16,920 --> 01:11:20,833
Naravno. Otici cu. Dok cekam da
me se bog seti,

490
01:11:20,960 --> 01:11:23,758
ja, Tuko Ramirez,
brat Ocar Ramireza,

491
01:11:23,880 --> 01:11:28,112
cu ti reci nesto.
Ti mislis da s bolji od mene.

492
01:11:28,240 --> 01:11:33,473
Jedan je postao svestenik... 
jedan bandit.

493
01:11:33,600 --> 01:11:37,309
Ti si izabrao tvoj put, ja svoj.
Moj je bio tezi.

494
01:11:37,440 --> 01:11:42,230
Ti pricas o roditeljima koje si ostavio
da bi postao svestenik. Ja sam ostao sa njima.

495
01:11:42,360 --> 01:11:46,353
Imao sam 10 or 12 godina. Ali sam ostao.

496
01:11:46,480 --> 01:11:48,516
Pokusao sam, ali nije islo.

497
01:11:48,640 --> 01:11:50,312
Jos nesto.

498
01:11:50,440 --> 01:11:56,037
Postao si pop zato sto si bio kukavica
da bi radio ono sto ja radim.

499
01:12:12,040 --> 01:12:13,393
Tuko.

500
01:12:22,560 --> 01:12:26,075
Molim te mi oprosti, brate.

501
01:12:54,400 --> 01:12:56,960
Ah, stomak mi je pun.

502
01:12:57,080 --> 01:12:59,992
Fini momak, moj brat.

503
01:13:00,120 --> 01:13:03,954
Nisam ti rekao da mi je brat
glavni ovde?

504
01:13:04,080 --> 01:13:07,993
Za sve. Kao Papa, skoro.
Samo on je u Rimu.

505
01:13:08,120 --> 01:13:12,272
Moj brat, rece,
"Ostani, ne vidjamo se."

506
01:13:12,400 --> 01:13:16,109
"Ima puno jela i pica.
Dovedi svog prijatelja."

507
01:13:16,240 --> 01:13:20,313
Kad god se vidimo, 
nikako me ne pusta.

508
01:13:20,480 --> 01:13:24,189
Moj brat, lud je zamnom!

509
01:13:26,720 --> 01:13:31,635
To ti je to. Iako sam skitnica,
sta god da se desi,

510
01:13:31,760 --> 01:13:37,596
znam da ovde imam brata koji 
nece odbiti bar da me nahrani.

511
01:13:39,440 --> 01:13:40,668
Naravno.

512
01:13:40,800 --> 01:13:45,396
Posle ukusnog obroka nema nista 
bolje od dobre cigare.

513
01:14:40,720 --> 01:14:42,233
Hoa!

514
01:14:50,480 --> 01:14:52,516
Ustaj.

515
01:14:52,640 --> 01:14:55,757
- Dolazi vojska.
- Plavi ili sivi?

516
01:15:02,520 --> 01:15:05,637
Sivi, kao mi.
Da se pozdravimo, pa da brisemo.

517
01:15:05,760 --> 01:15:09,719
Hura! Hura za Konfederaciju!

518
01:15:09,840 --> 01:15:12,752
Ura! Dole General Grant.

519
01:15:12,880 --> 01:15:14,598
Ura za Generala...

520
01:15:14,720 --> 01:15:16,153
- Kako se zvase?
- Li.

521
01:15:16,280 --> 01:15:17,508
Li!

522
01:15:18,120 --> 01:15:20,190
Hvala bogu. I On mrzi Jenkije.

523
01:15:21,160 --> 01:15:22,718
Hura!

524
01:15:22,840 --> 01:15:26,913
Bog nije na nasoj strani
zasto sto mrzi i idiote.

525
01:15:38,760 --> 01:15:44,710
Hop! 2, 3, 4!
Hop! 2, 3, 4!

526
01:15:46,520 --> 01:15:48,795
Ratni zarobljenici, napred

527
01:15:50,480 --> 01:15:52,596
mars!

528
01:15:52,720 --> 01:15:57,157
Hop! 2, 3, 4!
Hop! 2, 3, 4!

529
01:16:41,120 --> 01:16:43,509
Stoj!

530
01:16:46,520 --> 01:16:48,476
Na levo!

531
01:16:51,760 --> 01:16:53,751
U liniju. Mrdaj!

532
01:17:35,400 --> 01:17:37,834
- Dzonatan Ros.
- Prisutan.

533
01:17:46,800 --> 01:17:50,076
- Nataniel Saliven.
- Prisutan.

534
01:17:50,840 --> 01:17:52,512
Robert Klark.

535
01:17:52,640 --> 01:17:53,959
Prisutan.

536
01:17:54,280 --> 01:17:57,317
- Sam Ricmond.
- Prisutan.

537
01:17:59,480 --> 01:18:01,550
Bil Karson.

538
01:18:03,560 --> 01:18:05,994
Bil Karson?

539
01:18:07,560 --> 01:18:10,154
Rekoh Bil Karson!

540
01:18:10,280 --> 01:18:13,113
Beli, zar to nije Lepooki?

541
01:18:13,240 --> 01:18:15,629
Sta je s njim? Spava?

542
01:18:16,880 --> 01:18:18,074
Bil Karson!

543
01:18:18,240 --> 01:18:22,518
Aha. Budi ti Bil Karson.

544
01:18:22,680 --> 01:18:24,193
Bil Karson!

545
01:18:24,360 --> 01:18:26,794
Evo! Ja sam!

546
01:18:35,120 --> 01:18:39,398
Molim te, Karsone... Odgovori: prisutan.

547
01:18:40,240 --> 01:18:42,390
Sta si - gluv?

548
01:18:48,440 --> 01:18:51,193
Sad reci prisutan, Karsone.

549
01:18:53,000 --> 01:18:57,994
Volim... velike, debele ljude kao ti,
kada padnu, prave vise buke.

550
01:18:58,120 --> 01:19:01,032
A nekad i ne ustanu.

551
01:19:01,840 --> 01:19:02,875
Valas!

552
01:19:04,280 --> 01:19:06,350
To je dosta.

553
01:19:09,120 --> 01:19:10,235
narednice.

554
01:19:11,840 --> 01:19:14,638
Kapetan hoce odmah da vas vidi.

555
01:19:18,040 --> 01:19:20,600
Postaraj se da ova dvojica budu
dobro tretirani.

556
01:19:30,120 --> 01:19:33,669
Jesi cuo? Dobar tretman.

557
01:19:35,440 --> 01:19:37,556
Aha.

558
01:19:40,600 --> 01:19:44,070
Poslednji put, Narednice,
naredjujem vam da se

559
01:19:44,200 --> 01:19:47,476
zarobljenici tretiraju kao zarobljenici.

560
01:19:47,600 --> 01:19:49,955
Nema vise brutalnosti.

561
01:19:50,080 --> 01:19:54,039
Ima stotine zarobljenika i
samo nekoliko ljudi da ih cuvaju.

562
01:19:54,160 --> 01:19:56,310
Moram da steknem postovanje.

563
01:19:56,440 --> 01:20:01,150
Mislim da ces ga zadobiti
boljim tretmanom.

564
01:20:01,280 --> 01:20:04,909
Da li se tako dobro postupa prema 
nasima u Andersonvil kampu?

565
01:20:05,040 --> 01:20:07,554
Bas me briga sta rade tamo!

566
01:20:07,680 --> 01:20:14,153
Dok ja komandujem, zatvorenici nece
biti muceni, prevareni... ili ubijeni.

567
01:20:14,320 --> 01:20:16,436
Je li to optuzba?

568
01:20:16,560 --> 01:20:21,634
narednice, gangrena mi je napala
nogu, ne oci.

569
01:20:21,800 --> 01:20:25,588
Znam da se zatvorenici ovde pljackaju.

570
01:20:25,720 --> 01:20:28,678
Znam da ima sljama okolo,
pored kampa,

571
01:20:28,800 --> 01:20:31,792
koji ceka da neko iznese plen.

572
01:20:31,960 --> 01:20:36,670
Ali dok sam ja komadant, necu 
dozvoliti takav lopovluk. Je'l jasno?

573
01:20:38,200 --> 01:20:40,111
Da, gospodine.

574
01:20:40,320 --> 01:20:42,754
Dok ste vi komadant.

575
01:20:43,480 --> 01:20:45,755
Da, narednice.

576
01:20:47,640 --> 01:20:51,792
Znam da zbog ove noge necu jos dugo,

577
01:20:51,920 --> 01:20:58,439
ali se molim da izdrzim da izvedem
na vojni sud

578
01:20:58,600 --> 01:21:04,152
sve one koji omalovazavaju i blate
uniformu Unije.

579
01:21:08,280 --> 01:21:10,510
Srecno.

580
01:21:43,200 --> 01:21:46,988
Ti i ostali se bolje smirite
nekoliko dana.

581
01:21:47,120 --> 01:21:51,477
Zadrzacu ovo. Ti idi.
Valas ce te obavestiti.

582
01:22:00,480 --> 01:22:04,473
- Valas, dovedi mi Karsona.
- Odmah.

583
01:22:17,680 --> 01:22:22,117
Lepooki rece da se ne pojavljujemo
nekoliko dana.

584
01:22:22,240 --> 01:22:27,155
Bicemo dovoljno blizu da pratimo
dogadjaje. Osedlajte konje.

585
01:22:27,840 --> 01:22:29,193
Napred!

586
01:22:37,800 --> 01:22:40,758
Udji, Tako. Ne stidi se.

587
01:22:40,880 --> 01:22:43,713
Ovde nema formalnosti.

588
01:22:54,160 --> 01:22:56,594
Proslo je mnogo.

589
01:22:59,920 --> 01:23:03,629
Gladan si. Sedi. Jedi.

590
01:23:23,040 --> 01:23:25,110
Znao sam! Znao sam!

591
01:23:25,240 --> 01:23:28,835
U trenutku kad sam te video,rekoh

592
01:23:29,680 --> 01:23:32,353
"Vidi tu svinju, Lepookog."

593
01:23:33,360 --> 01:23:35,920
"Kladim se da je opet nasao
lak posao  

594
01:23:38,600 --> 01:23:43,993
- i da nikad ne zaboravlja prijatelja."
- Nikad ne zaboravljam stare prijatelje.

595
01:23:45,840 --> 01:23:47,114
Tacno!

596
01:23:47,240 --> 01:23:49,800
Lepo je videti opet stare prijatelje.

597
01:23:49,920 --> 01:23:51,114
Jeste!

598
01:23:51,800 --> 01:23:55,713
Narocito kad su dosli iz daleka.

599
01:23:55,840 --> 01:23:58,229
- I kad imaju toliko toga da ispricaju.
- Mm-hm.

600
01:23:58,360 --> 01:24:03,354
- A vi imate o cemu da pricate?
- Mm.

601
01:24:03,480 --> 01:24:10,830
- Zarobljeni ste blizu Fort Kreiga?
- Mm-hm.

602
01:24:10,960 --> 01:24:16,353
Ako ste bili pod Siblijem, to znaci
da ste dolazili iz Santa Fea.

603
01:24:17,520 --> 01:24:18,953
Mm-hm.

604
01:24:28,560 --> 01:24:33,509
- Da li je bilo tesko preci pustinju?
- Mm-hm. Vrlo. Mm.

605
01:24:33,640 --> 01:24:37,838
Narocito ako nemas nista za pice.

606
01:24:38,240 --> 01:24:42,392
Zasto se krijes pod imenom Bil Karson?

607
01:24:46,680 --> 01:24:49,911
To je ime kao i sva ostala.

608
01:24:50,120 --> 01:24:53,430
Nije pametno koristiti svoje ime.

609
01:24:53,840 --> 01:24:57,958
Kao ti.
Kladim se da te ne zovu Lepooki.

610
01:24:58,080 --> 01:25:00,594
Narednik Lepooki!

611
01:25:06,120 --> 01:25:11,114
Moze li malo muzike uz rucak?

612
01:25:11,240 --> 01:25:15,677
Muzika? Da, to je super.
Dobro je za probavu.

613
01:25:29,960 --> 01:25:34,317
- Znaci, Bil Karson je lazno ime, jeli?
- Aha.

614
01:25:37,360 --> 01:25:39,669
I ovo je lazno?

615
01:25:39,840 --> 01:25:44,356
Pise Bil Karson na njemu.

616
01:25:45,640 --> 01:25:48,996
Uzmi. To je Karsonov duvan.

617
01:27:08,120 --> 01:27:11,954
Da li je Karson bio ziv ili mrtav
kad si ga nasao?

618
01:27:17,240 --> 01:27:21,028
Sta ti je rekao o parama?

619
01:27:21,160 --> 01:27:26,359
Ne... Ne... Ne znam o cemu pricas...

620
01:27:43,400 --> 01:27:45,834
Osecajnije.

621
01:28:01,800 --> 01:28:06,430
Mozes se smatrati srecnijim nego
tvoj drugar.

622
01:28:06,560 --> 01:28:13,432
Valas udara dokle god traje pesma.
Mnogi od nas su bili na sesiji.

623
01:28:32,680 --> 01:28:35,478
Kako ti je sada probava?

624
01:28:38,520 --> 01:28:42,957
- Bolje pricaj.
- Nemam sta.

625
01:29:08,400 --> 01:29:10,755
Sviraj tu violinu!

626
01:29:51,800 --> 01:29:56,032
Ja... Ja... Pricacu. Pricacu!

627
01:30:04,720 --> 01:30:07,598
Sta je rekao o parama?

628
01:30:07,720 --> 01:30:13,556
Zakopano... zakop... zakopano je u 
grobu.

629
01:30:13,680 --> 01:30:15,955
Gde?

630
01:30:16,080 --> 01:30:20,039
Sed... Sed Hil Groblje.

631
01:30:22,720 --> 01:30:24,836
Koji grob?

632
01:30:25,520 --> 01:30:28,592
Ja... Ne znam.

633
01:30:31,520 --> 01:30:36,674
Beli... Beli...
On zna... ime groba.

634
01:30:52,320 --> 01:30:54,197
Rat je zavrsen za tebe.

635
01:30:57,840 --> 01:31:00,274
Obuci ovo.

636
01:31:03,080 --> 01:31:04,479
Zasto?

637
01:31:04,600 --> 01:31:06,989
Ideno na put.

638
01:31:08,520 --> 01:31:09,794
Gde?

639
01:31:09,960 --> 01:31:14,875
Da nadjemo $200,000.
Sada znam ime groblja.

640
01:31:15,000 --> 01:31:18,276
A ti znas ime groba.

641
01:31:36,680 --> 01:31:40,036
Necu dobiti isti tretman?

642
01:31:42,640 --> 01:31:44,710
Da li bi pricao?

643
01:31:45,640 --> 01:31:47,631
Ne. Verovatno ne.

644
01:31:48,120 --> 01:31:50,509
Tako sam i mislio.

645
01:31:50,640 --> 01:31:53,473
Nije da si tvrdji od Tuka,

646
01:31:53,600 --> 01:31:57,513
ali si dovoljno pametan da znas
da te prica nece spasiti.

647
01:32:00,720 --> 01:32:04,156
A Tuko? Je li...

648
01:32:04,280 --> 01:32:06,669
Mm-mm. Ne.

649
01:32:06,800 --> 01:32:08,711
Ne jos.

650
01:32:08,840 --> 01:32:11,195
Ali je u vrlo dobrim rukama.

651
01:32:11,880 --> 01:32:15,839
Promenio si partnere,
ali jos imas isti dogovor.

652
01:32:15,960 --> 01:32:18,269
Nisam poklepan. Uzimam samo pola.

653
01:32:18,400 --> 01:32:22,871
Dvojica nas je. Trebalo bi da
je lakse nego samo jednom.

654
01:32:27,600 --> 01:32:28,874
Aha.

655
01:32:48,640 --> 01:32:52,030
Mirno! To je to, ne  mrdajte.

656
01:32:52,480 --> 01:32:56,314
Sada, ne disite. Mirno... gotovo je.

657
01:32:56,920 --> 01:32:58,751
Imam je!

658
01:32:58,880 --> 01:33:00,279
Hvala!

659
01:33:14,000 --> 01:33:18,118
Bojis se da se ne izgubis?
Gde ce pobunjenik?

660
01:33:18,240 --> 01:33:20,959
U pakao, sa ucenom na glavi!

661
01:33:21,120 --> 01:33:25,830
$3,000. To je puna za glavu.

662
01:33:25,960 --> 01:33:29,430
Kladim se da ti nisu platili ni 
peni za ruku.

663
01:33:34,920 --> 01:33:41,553
Ako te ja sredim, trebace ti cudo
da ponovo ustanes.

664
01:34:00,720 --> 01:34:02,995
Srecniji si nego ovaj.

665
01:34:03,120 --> 01:34:06,237
Dobices konopac i gotovo.

666
01:34:06,360 --> 01:34:11,036
Ovaj put nema partner da te spasi!

667
01:34:32,240 --> 01:34:33,912
Penji se!

668
01:35:56,880 --> 01:36:00,759
Rado bi stavio sapu na to, ha?

669
01:36:01,440 --> 01:36:05,877
Hocu da pisam. U vozu sam skoro
deset sati.

670
01:36:06,000 --> 01:36:08,309
Vec smrdis kao svinja.

671
01:36:08,440 --> 01:36:11,398
Da ne pogorsavamo stvari.

672
01:36:13,080 --> 01:36:15,071
Polazi!

673
01:36:21,400 --> 01:36:25,757
Ne mogu dok gledas.

674
01:36:48,600 --> 01:36:52,036
Napravi si mnogo buke,prijatelju?

675
01:37:11,360 --> 01:37:15,558
Neces da raskines nase prijateljstvo?
E, ja cu!

676
01:38:55,400 --> 01:38:56,799
Vod, stani!

677
01:38:58,200 --> 01:39:00,077
Zauzmite mesta.

678
01:39:10,040 --> 01:39:11,758
Spremni!

679
01:39:12,800 --> 01:39:14,756
Nisani! Pali!

680
01:39:30,360 --> 01:39:33,272
Slim, pazi na konje.

681
01:43:38,040 --> 01:43:41,157
Trazio sam te osam meseci.

682
01:43:41,280 --> 01:43:44,875
Kad god sam imao pistolj u ruci,

683
01:43:45,000 --> 01:43:47,275
mislio sam na tebe.

684
01:43:47,400 --> 01:43:51,109
Sad te nalazim tacno u poziciji
koja mi odgovara.

685
01:43:51,240 --> 01:43:55,677
Imao sam dovoljno vremena da naucim
kako da pucam levom.

686
01:44:09,720 --> 01:44:13,349
Kad treba da pucas, pucaj! Ne pricaj!

687
01:44:15,640 --> 01:44:18,712
Svaki pistolj ima zvoj zvuk.

688
01:44:18,840 --> 01:44:21,479
Savrsen tajming, veliki.

689
01:44:38,320 --> 01:44:41,118
Klem, prati ga.

690
01:45:13,520 --> 01:45:15,397
Tut-tut-tut.

691
01:45:34,880 --> 01:45:37,758
Samo tren! Sad cu!

692
01:45:37,880 --> 01:45:42,112
Samo da se obucem i otvori cu.

693
01:46:00,920 --> 01:46:04,276
Oblaci prnje i skloni pistolj.

694
01:46:13,280 --> 01:46:19,435
Hej! Hej, Beli, kako si, dovraga,
pobegao iz onog svinjca?

695
01:46:20,000 --> 01:46:25,120
Na moj nacin.
Ovde sam s tvojim prijateljem Lepookim.

696
01:46:25,720 --> 01:46:28,951
Priznao si, izdajnice! Priznao si.

697
01:46:29,080 --> 01:46:34,074
Ne, nisam.
Da jesam, verovatno ne bi bio ovde.

698
01:46:35,680 --> 01:46:40,754
Ti... ja...
Znaci samo ti znas tvoju polovinu tajne?

699
01:46:41,120 --> 01:46:42,314
Mm-hm.

700
01:46:45,080 --> 01:46:51,428
Ah, Beli, Drago mi je da radis sa mnom,
opet smo zajedno!

701
01:46:51,560 --> 01:46:55,314
- Obuci cu se. Ubicu ga i vrati cu se.
- O, slusaj, uh...

702
01:46:55,440 --> 01:46:59,718
Zaboravio sam da pomenem... nije sam.

703
01:46:59,840 --> 01:47:04,709
- Petorica su.
- Petorica?

704
01:47:05,080 --> 01:47:07,150
Da.

705
01:47:09,000 --> 01:47:12,037
Znaci zato si dosao po Tuka.

706
01:47:14,000 --> 01:47:17,515
Nema veze. Pobicu ih sve.

707
01:47:28,200 --> 01:47:30,794
Ubili su ga iz blizine.

708
01:47:49,080 --> 01:47:51,116
Oho, gle ko je ovde.

709
01:47:51,240 --> 01:47:55,119
Tu je i drugi.

710
01:47:55,240 --> 01:47:58,118
Dolaze da nas traze.

711
01:47:58,240 --> 01:48:01,357
Pazi.

712
01:48:01,800 --> 01:48:04,075
Dvojica su.

713
01:48:04,560 --> 01:48:07,120
Hocu Belog zivog.

714
01:48:14,240 --> 01:48:18,597
Ti. Hajde, idemo.

715
01:48:50,800 --> 01:48:53,268
Hteo si da umres sam?

716
01:50:39,920 --> 01:50:40,796
Bu!

717
01:51:04,480 --> 01:51:07,074
Hej, Beli! Lepooki je moj.

718
01:51:07,200 --> 01:51:09,350
Vazi.

719
01:51:46,720 --> 01:51:50,793
"Vidimo se uskoro, i... idi..."

720
01:51:50,920 --> 01:51:53,388
- "Idioti."
- Ha?

721
01:51:53,520 --> 01:51:55,829
Za tebe.

722
01:52:19,400 --> 01:52:21,834
Kako mirno i tiho, amigo.

723
01:52:21,960 --> 01:52:24,838
Kao na groblju, na primer?

724
01:52:25,920 --> 01:52:29,071
Tamo treba da je most preko reke.

725
01:52:29,200 --> 01:52:33,193
- Bolje da cekamo mrak.
- Veruj mi, Beli!

726
01:52:34,680 --> 01:52:37,274
Imam dobar njuh.

727
01:52:37,400 --> 01:52:40,676
Tuko te je doveo ovoliko daleko,
I odvesu te do kra...

728
01:52:45,720 --> 01:52:48,280
- Reci kapetanu.
- Da, ser.

729
01:52:48,400 --> 01:52:51,198
Polazite. Za mnom.

730
01:53:34,840 --> 01:53:37,991
Nasli smo ih blizu, sir.

731
01:53:51,400 --> 01:53:53,516
Odakle si dosao?

732
01:53:54,440 --> 01:53:55,998
Ilinois.

733
01:53:56,960 --> 01:53:58,951
A ti?

734
01:53:59,080 --> 01:54:01,992
Ja... Ja sam sa njim.

735
01:54:06,840 --> 01:54:09,149
Zasto ste ovde?

736
01:54:10,560 --> 01:54:13,916
Hocemo... da se prikljucimo, Generale.

737
01:54:15,400 --> 01:54:18,710
Bolje da naucis rankove.

738
01:54:18,840 --> 01:54:20,876
Ja sam kapetan.

739
01:54:21,000 --> 01:54:22,877
Gubi se!

740
01:54:24,160 --> 01:54:27,596
Mozda je danas tvoj djavolji dan,
pa idi napisi nesto.

741
01:54:27,720 --> 01:54:29,711
Da, gospodine.

742
01:54:33,800 --> 01:54:36,109
Znaci, hocete da se prikljucite?

743
01:54:37,040 --> 01:54:40,396
Morate da prodjete test.

744
01:54:48,680 --> 01:54:50,716
Pa, da vidimo.

745
01:55:11,720 --> 01:55:17,556
Ti ces imati karijeru.
Najmanje do pukovnika.

746
01:55:17,680 --> 01:55:19,989
- Stvarno?
- Maravno!

747
01:55:20,120 --> 01:55:27,117
Sto kazu, imas sve kvalifikacije da
postanes ekspert za oruzje.

748
01:55:27,240 --> 01:55:32,394
Ovo je glavo oruzje u ratu.

749
01:55:33,840 --> 01:55:36,752
Borbeni moral je u ovoj boci.

750
01:55:37,400 --> 01:55:39,595
Dobrovoljci.

751
01:55:41,800 --> 01:55:45,793
Ocete da se prijavite, hm? 'Ajde.

752
01:55:46,240 --> 01:55:48,470
Idemo dole.

753
01:55:50,400 --> 01:55:53,870
Proba jos nije pocela.
Na vreme ste dosli.

754
01:55:54,160 --> 01:55:57,835
Uskoro mozete da se prikljucite herojima
Branston Mosta.

755
01:55:58,800 --> 01:56:00,756
Imamo dva napada na dan.

756
01:56:00,880 --> 01:56:03,394
- Dva napada dnevno?
- Da.

757
01:56:03,520 --> 01:56:08,640
Pobunjenici misle da je taj most
glavni u celoj oblasti.

758
01:56:08,760 --> 01:56:11,513
Glupi, beskorisni most!

759
01:56:11,640 --> 01:56:14,598
Mrlja na mapi.

760
01:56:14,720 --> 01:56:20,795
Stab je odlucio da moramo zauzeti
tu smesnu mrlju.

761
01:56:22,560 --> 01:56:24,596
Cak i da svi izginemo.

762
01:56:24,720 --> 01:56:28,759

763
01:56:28,880 --> 01:56:33,670
I to nije sve.
Obe strane hoce da sacuvaju most.

764
01:56:33,800 --> 01:56:38,828
Neostecenog ga hoce Jug,a i mi
ga hocemo celog.

765
01:56:40,760 --> 01:56:46,039
Sve ce da se rasturi,
ali jedno je sigurno, momci,

766
01:56:46,160 --> 01:56:49,311
Branston most ce ostati citav.

767
01:56:49,560 --> 01:56:54,076
Je li lose sto ovako pricam 
dobrovoljcima?

768
01:56:54,200 --> 01:56:57,510
Bio sam i gori.

769
01:57:01,560 --> 01:57:05,269
Sredio sam ga! Rasturio. Bum!

770
01:57:06,280 --> 01:57:09,158
Unutra! Sve sam unistio.

771
01:57:10,080 --> 01:57:15,074
Za vojni sud je sanjati o unistenju.
Ozbiljan zlocin.

772
01:57:15,200 --> 01:57:19,751
Cak i misliti o unistenju mosta je...

773
01:57:21,920 --> 01:57:24,115
Zasto ga stvarno ne rasturiti, Kaptane?

774
01:57:26,000 --> 01:57:28,912
Kapetane, nije to nista.
Da ih uplasimo.

775
01:57:32,400 --> 01:57:35,198
Sanjao sam o tome!

776
01:57:37,960 --> 01:57:40,997
Smislio sam plan.

777
01:57:41,120 --> 01:57:42,951
Jesam!

778
01:57:44,120 --> 01:57:46,793
Najbolje je posle napada.

779
01:57:46,920 --> 01:57:50,435
Kad je primirije,
skupljaju ranjene.

780
01:57:50,560 --> 01:57:54,599
Kad bi to mogao,
spasao bih stotine ljudi.

781
01:58:00,760 --> 01:58:03,433
Ali mi fali hrabrosti.

782
01:58:08,240 --> 01:58:11,391
Pocinju dnevnu klanicu na vreme.

783
01:58:11,520 --> 01:58:15,149
Kapetane, sve cete cekaju vase naredbe.

784
01:58:15,280 --> 01:58:17,396
Evo me odmah.

785
01:58:29,560 --> 01:58:31,596
Haj'mo.

786
01:58:31,720 --> 01:58:35,633
Prijatelji, pridruzite se spektaklu.

787
01:59:05,880 --> 01:59:07,836
Cete, izvestaj!

788
01:59:08,600 --> 01:59:10,079
Ceta B - spremna!

789
01:59:11,360 --> 01:59:13,271
Ceta E - spremna!

790
01:59:14,120 --> 01:59:15,633
Ceta D - spremna!

791
01:59:21,800 --> 01:59:23,870
Cete, juris!

792
01:59:44,840 --> 01:59:48,958
Hej, Beli! Izgleda da Kapetan trazi
metak za svoju hrabrost.

793
01:59:49,080 --> 01:59:51,036
Aha.

794
02:00:41,640 --> 02:00:44,791
Nikad nisam video toliko protracenih
ljudi.

795
02:01:03,920 --> 02:01:07,549
Imam osecaj da ce to biti dobra,
duga borba.

796
02:01:11,280 --> 02:01:12,872
- Beli.

797
02:01:13,000 --> 02:01:15,992
Novac je s druge strane reke.

798
02:01:16,400 --> 02:01:18,356
O? Gde?

799
02:01:21,280 --> 02:01:24,317
Amigo, rekao sam s druge strane,
to je dovoljno.

800
02:01:25,200 --> 02:01:28,988
Ali dok su Juznjaci tamo,
ne mozemo preci.

801
02:01:29,120 --> 02:01:33,716
Sta bi bilo kad bi neko ipak
unistio most?

802
02:01:34,960 --> 02:01:39,431
Onda bi ovi idioti otisli negde
drugde da se biju.

803
02:01:40,480 --> 02:01:42,152
Mozda.

804
02:02:17,400 --> 02:02:20,597
Doktora, brzo! Kapetan je ranjen!

805
02:02:22,880 --> 02:02:25,599
Brzo, nosila!

806
02:02:27,440 --> 02:02:28,998
Polako! Polako.

807
02:02:38,760 --> 02:02:41,320
Spremite stvari.

808
02:02:59,680 --> 02:03:02,319
Malo ovoga ce pomoci.

809
02:03:09,040 --> 02:03:10,996
Uzmite gutljaj ovoga, Kapetane.

810
02:03:11,360 --> 02:03:13,316
Drzite oci otvorene.

811
02:03:58,920 --> 02:04:03,471
Sta to radite?
Ne. Ostavite me!

812
02:05:38,360 --> 02:05:41,955
Beli, hej!
Shvatas li da rizikujemo zivote?

813
02:05:42,080 --> 02:05:47,200
Aha. Ako poginem, nikad neces
dobiti onaj divni novac.

814
02:05:47,320 --> 02:05:49,788
- Huh?
- Da, Tuko.

815
02:05:49,920 --> 02:05:51,876
Stvarno bi bila steta.

816
02:06:21,800 --> 02:06:22,755
Doktore...

817
02:06:25,240 --> 02:06:29,791
Doktore... Ako mi mozes jos
malo pomoci,

818
02:06:29,920 --> 02:06:32,388
ocekuj dobre vesti.

819
02:06:44,040 --> 02:06:47,077
Zasto ne bi jedan drugom rekli 
svoje polovine tajne?

820
02:06:47,200 --> 02:06:48,519
Zasto da ne?

821
02:06:50,080 --> 02:06:52,275
Ti prvi.

822
02:06:54,160 --> 02:06:59,792
Ne. Mislim da je nolje... uh...
ti pocni.

823
02:07:04,200 --> 02:07:05,997
Vazi.

824
02:07:07,600 --> 02:07:09,591
Ime groblja je..

825
02:07:27,440 --> 02:07:29,476
Sed Hil! Sad je tvoj red!

826
02:07:34,640 --> 02:07:36,232
Uh-huh.

827
02:07:36,920 --> 02:07:39,992
Ime groba je

828
02:07:43,280 --> 02:07:45,316
Arc Stanton.

829
02:07:45,480 --> 02:07:50,076
Arch... Arch Stanton? Jesi siguran?

830
02:07:50,200 --> 02:07:53,192
Aha. Naravno.

831
02:13:51,880 --> 02:13:53,598
Hah!

832
02:19:09,040 --> 02:19:11,474
Bilo bi lakse sa ovim.

833
02:19:50,200 --> 02:19:52,714
Dvojica mogu da kopaju brze
nego jedan.

834
02:19:52,840 --> 02:19:54,034
Kopaj.

835
02:19:56,560 --> 02:19:58,869
Ti ne kopas.

836
02:20:10,160 --> 02:20:13,709
Ako me ubijes,
neces videti ni centa.

837
02:20:15,600 --> 02:20:17,158
Zasto?

838
02:20:18,880 --> 02:20:20,757
Reci cu ti zasto.

839
02:20:22,840 --> 02:20:24,956
Zato sto tu nema niceg.

840
02:20:32,360 --> 02:20:35,875
- Kurv...
- Mislio si da ti verujem?

841
02:20:38,400 --> 02:20:40,868
$200,000 je puno para.

842
02:20:42,520 --> 02:20:45,080
Moracemo da ga zaradimo.

843
02:20:47,440 --> 02:20:48,589
Kako?

844
02:20:59,200 --> 02:21:02,636
Napisacu ime na dnu ovog kamena.

845
02:21:06,400 --> 02:21:08,311
Pistolj?

846
02:26:59,240 --> 02:27:03,199
Svinjo! Hoces da poginem?
Kad si ga ispraznio?

847
02:27:04,640 --> 02:27:06,551
Sinoc.

848
02:27:06,680 --> 02:27:11,356
Vidis, na svetu ima dve vrste ljudi.

849
02:27:11,480 --> 02:27:15,758
Oni sa napunjenim pistoljima
i oni koji kopaju.

850
02:27:15,880 --> 02:27:18,997
- Ti kopaj.
- Gde?

851
02:27:30,120 --> 02:27:31,599
Ovde.

852
02:27:32,360 --> 02:27:34,920
"Nep... p... poz..."

853
02:27:35,040 --> 02:27:36,519
Nema imena!

854
02:27:37,840 --> 02:27:40,479
Ni ovde.

855
02:27:40,640 --> 02:27:44,076
E vidis, to mi je rekao Bil Karson.

856
02:27:44,200 --> 02:27:49,228
Grob bez imena, odmah pored
Arc Stanton.

857
02:27:49,720 --> 02:27:50,675
?

858
02:27:55,440 --> 02:27:57,556
Pozuri.

859
02:28:52,760 --> 02:28:54,990
Pare! Sve je nase! Pare!

860
02:29:10,240 --> 02:29:13,073
Salis se, Beli. Ne bi valjda.

861
02:29:13,200 --> 02:29:15,555
Ne bi se tako salio sa mnom.

862
02:29:15,680 --> 02:29:18,069
Nije sala. To je konopac, Tuko.

863
02:29:18,200 --> 02:29:23,069
Hocu da se popnes gore
i da stavis glavu u omcu.

864
02:30:27,720 --> 02:30:28,914
Pa, sad...

865
02:30:29,040 --> 02:30:31,349
Izgleda bas kao nekada.

866
02:30:35,760 --> 02:30:37,273
Cetiri za tebe.

867
02:30:39,520 --> 02:30:45,277
I cetiri ... cetiri za mene.

868
02:31:11,120 --> 02:31:12,439
Hej, Bel...

869
02:31:12,560 --> 02:31:13,754
Bel... Beli...

870
02:31:22,800 --> 02:31:24,791
Hej, Be... li...!

871
02:31:26,120 --> 02:31:28,076
Zao mi je, Tuko.

872
02:31:31,440 --> 02:31:32,759
Beli!

873
02:31:41,640 --> 02:31:43,153
Beli!!

874
02:31:51,000 --> 02:31:52,319
Beli!

875
02:32:02,840 --> 02:32:03,795
Beli!

876
02:32:13,960 --> 02:32:14,949
Blon...

877
02:32:30,560 --> 02:32:32,915
Beli!!

878
02:32:58,440 --> 02:33:00,192
Beli!

879
02:33:57,600 --> 02:34:00,353
Hej, Beli!

880
02:34:01,160 --> 02:34:04,197
Znas sta si ti?

881
02:34:07,520 --> 02:34:10,637
Samo obican kuck...

